headline: General Industrial Machinery Stocks Q3 Results: Benchmarking General Electric (NYSE:GE)
summary: As the Q3 earnings season comes to a close, it’s time to take stock of this quarter’s best and worst performers in the general industrial machinery industry, including General Electric (NYSE:GE) and its peers.
